{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":44,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"你要带我到哪里去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":7,"line_start":4,"line_end":4},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"带你回家去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":7,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"回家？我哪里有家？","tone":"疑问","chapter":7,"line_start":8,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"你有的。我相信你一定会以你的家为荣，你的家也一定会以你为荣。","tone":"认真","chapter":7,"line_start":10,"line_end":11},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"以我为荣？像我这么样一个已经从头顶坏到脚底坏透子的坏小孩？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":7,"line_start":14,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"你不坏。","tone":"陈述","chapter":7,"line_start":18,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"我还不坏？怎么样才算坏？","tone":"疑问","chapter":7,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"能做得出那种卑鄙无耻下流的事的人才算坏。可是你做不出。","tone":"认真","chapter":7,"line_start":22,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"李坏","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"你怎么知道我做不出？","tone":"疑问","chapter":7,"line_start":26,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"因为你是李家的人，是李家的骨血。","tone":"严肃","chapter":7,"line_start":28,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"只要你能保持这一点骨气，我也敢保证世界上绝没有任何人敢对你有一点轻贱。","tone":"严肃","chapter":7,"line_start":30,"line_end":32}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_li_huai","name":"李坏","alias":["坏小孩"],"identity":"李家后人","faction":"李家","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"李家骨血，自认坏透却本质不坏的少年","personality":{"traits":["自卑","叛逆","自嘲","倔强","敏感"],"spee